@startuml seq_submit_leave_request
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Submit Leave Request Flow

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Staff" as Staff
participant "React SPA (Staff)" as ClientStaff
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Leave Service" as Leave
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG
database "MongoDB" as Mongo
participant "Socket.IO / Redis" as Socket
participant "React SPA (Manager)" as ClientManager

Staff -> ClientStaff : Fill out leave form & Click Submit
ClientStaff -> Gateway : POST /api/leaves
Gateway -> Leave : Route Request

Leave -> Leave : Verify JWT Token
Leave -> PG : Validate Business Logic \n(Leave balance, daily absence limit)

alt Invalid Logic (Exceeds limit/continuous days)
    Leave -> ClientStaff : 400 Bad Request (With Error Message)
else Valid Request
    Leave -> PG : INSERT INTO leave_requests \n(status = 'PENDING')
    Leave -> Mongo : INSERT LeaveLog \n(Action: CREATE)
    Leave -> Socket : io.emit("new_leave_request", target: Manager)
    Leave -> ClientStaff : 201 Created (Submitted successfully)
    
    Socket -> ClientManager : Push Event "new_leave_request"
    ClientManager -> ClientManager : Increment Notification Badge & Show Toast
end
@enduml